page.title: 06BREEDING FISH
page.content:
You can get many types of indoor or outdoor fish from dealers.The most common of these are the out door fish, because they are very cheap.
My hobby is breeding fish.I have many different types but mostly{goldfish because they are less expensive.
We also have some expensive fish. The most expensive fish you can get are the{Koi}because no two fish have the same markings.
I also have some{Orfe.}These fish are long and golden in colour. My Blue Orfe I obtained from a{fish {farm}as they do not breed in England.
